title: Keun Ruk Salub Chata
overview: Wat is a famous celebrity who is dating a famous model named Ginney. Tet is a famous pilot who is in a relationship with a doctor named Kulanji. But one day, the body of Wat and Tet have switched. As Tet and Wat have totally different occupation, how will they handle the situation? Will Ginney and Kulanji notice the truth?
